employed\nin many safety critical systems subject to structured uncertainty and are thus\nrelevant for cyber-physical applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Feb 2013 20:31:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-18"}
