is not needed at practical\napplications but it is shown for the sake of ongoing discussions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Feb 2013 21:58:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2013 15:37:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-18"}
